# Retail-Sales-Forecasting-Segmentation-Dashboard

1.Create the Project Structure

Retail-Sales-Analytics-Dashboard/
│
├── data/
│   └── retail_sales.csv
│
├── notebooks/
│   └── EDA.ipynb
│
├── dashboard/
│   └── app.py
│
├── reports/
│   └── sales_report.xlsx
│
├── screenshots/
│   ├── dashboard_home.png
│   ├── sales_analysis.png
│   └── customer_segments.png
│
├── requirements.txt
├── README.md
└── .gitignore

2: Upload Your Dataset

Place your retail dataset in:

data/retail_sales.csv

Dataset should have approximately:

9994 rows
21 columns

Examples:

Order ID
Product
Category
Region
Sales
Profit
Quantity
Discount
Order Date
Customer ID
